        "brief_summary": {
            "textblock": "The investigators believe that patients with Crohn's disease are able to report details of\n      their own medical history accurately and record changes in clinical status effectively over\n      time.  Using an internet-based database the investigators will ask patients to report their\n      own disease history, and the investigators will compare their reports to the medical record."
        }, 
